@NODE V22 "Latest News in v2.2"
@{b}Latest News in Version 2.2@{ub}

    Hi!

    After one and a half years I can finally present you a new
    version of the most beloved GUI for WarpSNES and SNES9x: The
    SNES9xGUI. This version was made on request by Steffen Häuser
    as he needed a GUI that would set the ChunkyPPC preferences
    for WarpSNES. SNES9xGUI does this now, although it hasn't been
    tested. 
  
    Additionally there's now a Swedish catalog included.

    Have fun,

             Andreas

    --
    Andreas Falkenhahn (aka Software Failure of Airsoft Softwair)
    Coder, Powered up with Amiga 1200T, Blizzard T-ERC 68040,
    http://airsoft.home.pages.de, ICQ: 42908277, IRC: SFA

@ENDNODE

