v1.0 Final (Monday August 10th)

· GUI can now be fully controlled by keyboard
· added AboutText
· some small code optimizations + fixes
· GUI was tested on A1200/040 AGA and A4000/040 CGFX
· updated GUI.readme to a little doc file
· added GadTools menu to the GUI
· added a little early ROM editor which currently only allows you
