v1.0 Beta 2 (Monday July 27th):

· added new options to the MUI GUI: Sound/NoSound (although sound isn`t supported yet)
                                    Enable internal Speedhacks
· redesigned the MUI GUI because its size was bigger than 256 (height of a HighRes screen)
· added Super Nintendo® logo to the GUI
· added Emulation Info to the GUI: Executablesize expanded to 68kb because of the included
                                   320x256x8 bitmap for the info !!
· added online bubblehelp
· GUI now requires PolarSmall.font in local Fonts: drawer, an assign Fonts: is automatically
  added to the actual fonts directory at start
 
v1.0 Beta 1 (Sunday July 26th, done in 2 hours):

· settings are saved automatically when quitting the program
· added MUI GUI with following options: Select ROM
					Frame skip (is this really useful on PPC :))?
					Enable/Disable H·DMA emulation
					Swap BG priorities
					Force LoRom/HiRom
					Show FPS
					No second joystick
					Hi/LoRes Screen
 					Hi/LoColor Screen
· works with other ports too: simply change executable in tooltypes
· added 2 color icon :D
· requires asl.library for ROM requester and muimaster.library for GUI

